                     <interp inst="t18040111-33-off201" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18040111-33-off201" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18040111-33-cd202" type="crimeDate">26th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040111-33-off201 t18040111-33-cd202"></join>, two pieces of cotton, containing together nine yards, value 1 l. 12 s. the property of 
                     
